metadata.description: Airdropped items can be unlocked and traded on https://apecoinrnarketplace.com/unlock. The Sad Ape Yacht Club(SAYC) is a collection of 1,000 unique Sad Ape NFTs. The SAYC pool lets you stake up to 1,082 $APE for each SAYC you own. By using this pool, you will be rewarded with 0.003 $APE per 24 hours. Airdropped items are locked and can be traded and staked after unlocking.
